-- ‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á Roblox ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏à‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô
local Players = game:GetService("Players") -- ‡∏î‡∏∂‡∏á‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ Players ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡πà‡∏ô
local TweenService = game:GetService("TweenService") -- ‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö Animation ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö smooth
local UserInputService = game:GetService("UserInputService") -- ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö Input ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ (Mouse/Touch)
local HttpService = game:GetService("HttpService") -- ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö JSON encode/decode ‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö Config
local RunService = game:GetService("RunService") -- ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö real-time

-- ‡∏î‡∏∂‡∏á LocalPlayer (‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡πà‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡∏ô‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ) ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ PlayerGui (‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö UI)
local Player = Players.LocalPlayer
local PlayerGui = Player:WaitForChild("PlayerGui") -- WaitForChild ‡∏õ‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô error ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏£‡πá‡∏à

-- ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á ScreenGui ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏Å (Container ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î)
local ScreenGui = Instance.new("ScreenGui")
ScreenGui.Name = "FierceExecutor" -- ‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏∏‡πÉ‡∏ô game.CoreGui
ScreenGui.ResetOnSpawn = false -- ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏Ñ‡∏±‡∏ç! ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ UI ‡∏´‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏ô respawn
ScreenGui.ZIndexBehavior = Enum.ZIndexBehavior.Sibling -- ‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏° layering ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á UI
ScreenGui.Parent = PlayerGui -- ‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö PlayerGui ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡πà‡∏ô

-- ========== ‡∏ò‡∏µ‡∏°‡∏™‡∏µ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏Å ==========
-- ‡∏™‡∏µ‡∏™‡πâ‡∏°‡∏î‡∏∏‡∏î‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏™‡πÑ‡∏ï‡∏•‡πå Fierce
local DarkBase = Color3.fromRGB(30, 10, 0) -- ‡∏™‡∏µ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏°
local MainColor = Color3.fromRGB(255, 90, 20) -- ‡∏™‡∏µ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏™‡∏î‡πÉ‡∏™
local DarkColor = Color3.fromRGB(200, 50, 0) -- ‡∏™‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏°‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°
local AccentColor = Color3.fromRGB(255, 140, 50) -- ‡∏™‡∏µ Accent ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö highlight
local Transparent = 0.12 -- ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÇ‡∏õ‡∏£‡πà‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏™‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏ô

-- ‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤ Tween (Animation)
local TweenInfoSmooth = TweenInfo.new(
    0.35, -- ‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏•‡∏≤ 0.35 ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏µ
    Enum.EasingStyle.Sine, -- ‡∏•‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏©‡∏ì‡∏∞‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏Ñ‡∏•‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö Sine (‡∏ô‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏•)
    Enum.EasingDirection.Out -- ‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏£‡πá‡∏ß ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏•‡∏á‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏ó‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢
)

-- ‡∏Ç‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏î GUI ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏° Maximize
local NormalSize = UDim2.new(0, 600, 0, 480) -- ‡∏Ç‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏î‡∏õ‡∏Å‡∏ï‡∏¥
local LargeSize = UDim2.new(0, 900, 0, 650) -- ‡∏Ç‡∏¢‡∏≤‡∏¢‡πÉ‡∏´‡∏ç‡πà
local NormalPos = UDim2.new(0.5, -300, 0.5, -240) -- Position ‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏õ‡∏Å‡∏ï‡∏¥
local LargePos = UDim2.new(0.5, -450, 0.5, -325) -- Position ‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏Ç‡∏¢‡∏≤‡∏¢

-- ========== Main Frame (‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏Å) ==========
local MainFrame = Instance.new("Frame")
MainFrame.Name = "MainFrame" -- ‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö debug
MainFrame.Size = NormalSize -- ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏Ç‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏î‡∏õ‡∏Å‡∏ï‡∏¥‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏ô
MainFrame.Position = NormalPos -- ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏à‡∏≠
MainFrame.BackgroundColor3 = DarkBase -- ‡∏™‡∏µ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á
MainFrame.BackgroundTransparency = Transparent -- ‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÇ‡∏õ‡∏£‡πà‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏™
MainFrame.BorderSizePixel = 0 -- ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏ö
MainFrame.ClipsDescendants = true -- ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏î‡∏™‡πà‡∏ß‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏Å‡∏¥‡∏ô (‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏Ñ‡∏±‡∏ç‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö animation)
MainFrame.Visible = true -- ‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á‡∏ú‡∏•
MainFrame.Parent = ScreenGui -- ‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤ ScreenGui

-- ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏° Gradient ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á‡∏™‡∏ß‡∏¢‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏°
local MainGradient = Instance.new("UIGradient")
MainGradient.Color = ColorSequence.new({
    ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(0, DarkBase), -- ‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏¢‡∏™‡∏µ DarkBase
    ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(1, MainColor) -- ‡∏à‡∏ö‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏¢‡∏™‡∏µ MainColor
})
MainGradient.Rotation = 30 -- ‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏á 30 ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏®‡∏≤
MainGradient.Parent = MainFrame

-- ‡∏°‡∏∏‡∏°‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏á‡∏°‡∏ô
local MainCorner = Instance.new("UICorner")
MainCorner.CornerRadius = UDim.new(0, 14) -- ‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏á 14px
MainCorner.Parent = MainFrame

-- Glow Effect ‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏ö‡πÜ
local MainGlow = Instance.new("UIStroke")
MainGlow.Transparency = 0.6
MainGlow.Color = AccentColor -- ‡∏™‡∏µ Accent
MainGlow.Thickness = 2 -- ‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏≤ 2px
MainGlow.Parent = MainFrame

-- ========== Notification System (‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö‡πÅ‡∏à‡πâ‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ô) ==========
-- ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ queue ‡πÅ‡∏ó‡∏ô global variable ‡∏õ‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô overlap
local NotificationQueue = {} -- Queue ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö notification
local NotifYPosition = 20 -- Y ‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏ô

-- ‡∏ü‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á Notification
local function ShowNotification(text, duration)
    duration = duration or 3 -- ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏ô 3 ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏µ
    
    -- ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á Frame ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö notification
    local notif = Instance.new("TextLabel")
    notif.Name = "Notification" -- ‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö debug
    notif.Size = UDim2.new(0, 300, 0, 50) -- ‡∏Ç‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏î
    notif.Position = UDim2.new(1, 320, 0, NotifYPosition) -- ‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏Ç‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏à‡∏≠
    notif.BackgroundColor3 = DarkBase -- ‡∏™‡∏µ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á
    notif.BackgroundTransparency = 0.2
    notif.BorderSizePixel = 0
    notif.Text = " " .. text -- ‡πÄ‡∏ß‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏£‡∏£‡∏Ñ‡∏ã‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏ô
    notif.TextColor3 = AccentColor -- ‡∏™‡∏µ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°
    notif.TextSize = 16
    notif.Font = Enum.Font.GothamBold -- ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏≤
    notif.TextXAlignment = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left -- ‡∏ä‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ã‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢
    notif.ZIndex = 1000 -- ‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà‡∏ö‡∏ô‡∏™‡∏∏‡∏î
    notif.Parent = ScreenGui
    
    -- ‡∏°‡∏∏‡∏°‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏á
    local corner = Instance.new("UICorner")
    corner.CornerRadius = UDim.new(0, 8)
    corner.Parent = notif
    
    -- Glow ‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏ö‡πÜ
    local stroke = Instance.new("UIStroke")
    stroke.Color = AccentColor
    stroke.Thickness = 2
    stroke.Transparency = 0.6
    stroke.Parent = notif
    
    -- ‡πÑ‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏î‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏ã‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢
    local icon = Instance.new("TextLabel")
    icon.Size = UDim2.new(0, 30, 0, 30)
    icon.Position = UDim2.new(0, 10, 0.5, -15) -- ‡∏Å‡∏∂‡πà‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á
    icon.BackgroundTransparency = 1
    icon.Text = "üíÄ" -- ‡πÑ‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏Å‡∏∞‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏Å
    icon.TextScaled = true
    icon.TextColor3 = AccentColor
    icon.Font = Enum.Font.GothamBlack
    icon.Parent = notif
    
    -- ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏° Y position ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö notification ‡∏ñ‡∏±‡∏î‡πÑ‡∏õ
    NotifYPosition = NotifYPosition + 60
    
    -- Animation ‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤ (‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏Ç‡∏ß‡∏≤)
    TweenService:Create(notif, TweenInfoSmooth, {
        Position = UDim2.new(1, -270, 0, notif.Position.Y.Offset)
    }):Play()
    
    -- ‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏•‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏Å
    spawn(function()
        wait(duration) -- ‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏° duration
        
        -- Animation ‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏Å (‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏Ç‡∏ß‡∏≤)
        TweenService:Create(notif, TweenInfoSmooth, {
            Position = UDim2.new(1, 320, 0, notif.Position.Y.Offset)
        }):Play()
        
        wait(0.4) -- ‡∏£‡∏≠ animation ‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏£‡πá‡∏à
        
        notif:Destroy() -- ‡∏•‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å memory
        NotifYPosition = NotifYPosition - 60 -- ‡∏•‡∏î Y ‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏±‡∏ö
    end)
    
    return notif -- Return ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏°
end

-- ========== Global Configuration (‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏±‡πà‡∏ß‡πÑ‡∏õ) ==========
-- ‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡πÉ‡∏ô table ‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß‡∏õ‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô global pollution
local FierceConfig = {
    WalkSpeed = 50,
    JumpPower = 50,
    ESP = {
        NameEnabled = false,
        HighlightEnabled = false,
        Range = 500,
        TextSize = 10
    },
    Visuals = {
        FOV = 70,
        Fullbright = false,
        NoFog = false,
        Crosshair = false
    }
}

-- ========== Utility Functions (‡∏ü‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ß‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠) ==========
-- ‡∏î‡∏∂‡∏á Character ‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏î‡∏†‡∏±‡∏¢ ‡∏õ‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô nil
local function GetCharacter()
    local char = Player.Character
    if not char or not char.Parent then -- ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤ nil ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ attach ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö workspace
        char = Player.CharacterAdded:Wait() -- ‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏à‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡∏à‡∏∞ spawn
    end
    return char
end

-- ‡∏î‡∏∂‡∏á Humanoid ‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏î‡∏†‡∏±‡∏¢
local function GetHumanoid()
    local char = GetCharacter()
    return char and char:FindFirstChildOfClass("Humanoid") -- Return nil ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡πÄ‡∏à‡∏≠
end

-- ‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏∂‡∏Å Config ‡∏•‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå
local function SaveConfiguration()
    pcall(function() -- pcall ‡∏õ‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô error ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤ writefile ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ (‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏ô Studio)
        if writefile then -- ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πá‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤ executor ‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö writefile ‡πÑ‡∏´‡∏°
            local configData = {
                ws = FierceConfig.WalkSpeed,
                jp = FierceConfig.JumpPower,
                esp_range = FierceConfig.ESP.Range,
                esp_textsize = FierceConfig.ESP.TextSize
            }
            writefile("fierce_config_v16.json", HttpService:JSONEncode(configData))
        end
    end)
end

-- ‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏î Config ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå
local function LoadConfiguration()
    pcall(function()
        if readfile and isfile and isfile("fierce_config_v16.json") then -- ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πá‡∏Ñ‡∏ü‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏ö
            local data = readfile("fierce_config_v16.json")
            local config = HttpService:JSONDecode(data)
            
            -- ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏Å‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô assign (‡∏õ‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô corrupted data)
            FierceConfig.WalkSpeed = (type(config.ws) == "number" and config.ws >= 0 and config.ws <= 500) and config.ws or 50
            FierceConfig.JumpPower = (type(config.jp) == "number" and config.jp >= 0 and config.jp <= 500) and config.jp or 50
            FierceConfig.ESP.Range = (type(config.esp_range) == "number" and config.esp_range > 0) and config.esp_range or 500
            FierceConfig.ESP.TextSize = (type(config.esp_textsize) == "number" and config.esp_textsize > 0) and config.esp_textsize or 10
            
            ShowNotification("‚úÖ Configuration loaded", 2)
        end
    end)
end

-- ‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏Å Load ‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏ô‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏î script
LoadConfiguration()

-- ========== Header (‡∏™‡πà‡∏ß‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á GUI) ==========
local Header = Instance.new("Frame")
Header.Name = "Header"
Header.Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 60) -- ‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏™‡∏π‡∏á 60px, ‡∏Å‡∏ß‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏ï‡πá‡∏°
Header.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.new(1,1,1) -- ‡∏™‡∏µ‡∏Ç‡∏≤‡∏ß‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö gradient
Header.BackgroundTransparency = 0.2
Header.BorderSizePixel = 0
Header.Parent = MainFrame -- ‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤ MainFrame

-- Gradient ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö header
local HeaderGradient = Instance.new("UIGradient")
HeaderGradient.Color = ColorSequence.new({
    ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(0, DarkColor), -- ‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏¢ DarkColor
    ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(1, DarkBase) -- ‡∏à‡∏ö‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏¢ DarkBase
})
HeaderGradient.Rotation = -30 -- ‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏á‡∏•‡∏ö 30 ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏®‡∏≤
HeaderGradient.Parent = Header

-- ‡∏°‡∏∏‡∏°‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏á
local HeaderCorner = Instance.new("UICorner")
HeaderCorner.CornerRadius = UDim.new(0, 14)
HeaderCorner.Parent = Header

-- ‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠ Script
local TitleLabel = Instance.new("TextLabel")
TitleLabel.Name = "TitleLabel"
TitleLabel.Size = UDim2.new(1, -200, 1, 0) -- ‡πÄ‡∏ß‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡∏î‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏Ç‡∏ß‡∏≤
TitleLabel.Position = UDim2.new(0, 70, 0, 0) -- ‡∏ä‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ã‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢ 70px (‡πÄ‡∏ß‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÇ‡∏•‡πÇ‡∏Å‡πâ)
TitleLabel.BackgroundTransparency = 1
TitleLabel.Text = ScriptName
TitleLabel.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1,1,1) -- ‡∏™‡∏µ‡∏Ç‡∏≤‡∏ß
TitleLabel.TextSize = 26
TitleLabel.Font = Enum.Font.GothamBlack -- ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏≤
TitleLabel.Parent = Header

-- ‡πÇ‡∏•‡πÇ‡∏Å‡πâ‡πÑ‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏ô
local LogoLabel = Instance.new("TextLabel")
